# Ansimate CLA signers
# ---------------------
# One Git-hosting username per line = the account that opens pull requests.
# By adding your username here you accept the Contributor License Agreement in CLA.md
# for your present and future contributions.
#
# Blank lines and lines starting with "#" are ignored.
# The pull-request check in .gitea/workflows/cla.yml compares the PR author against this list
